content: Hmm yeah
I made a list again last night
I want a guy who never leaves his socks around
Knows the words to all the songs I sing too loud
He text back fast but not too fast like chill
And laughs at my jokes even when they kill
If I could stitch a perfect plan
Mix a little will of peter pan
Give him jeans and not a suit
Someone weird but kinda cute
Guess I gotta build my dream from scratch
Draw his smile then give it a patch
Plug him in and hope he runs
Call it love or just for fun
No wires no sparks just vibes that click
If he's a mess I'll hit unpick
Franken boy with better taste
No monster just a pretty face
He won't ghost me when the group chat hits
Knows the snack eyes where a romance lives
Can drive a bike but still can't cook
And never says go read a book
Guess I gotta build my dream from scratch
Draw his smile then give it a patch
Plug him in and hope he runs
Call it love or just for fun
No eyes no sparks just vibes that click
If he's a mess I'll hit unpick
Franken boy with better taste
No monster just a pretty face
Maybe he's out there or maybe not so
Till then I'll take my shot
Sewing up my perfect find
Stuck inside my d I mind
